WEBVTT

00:00.581 --> 00:03.224
I will persuade Ferrante
no alliance with Sixtus

00:03.225 --> 00:05.493
ever benefits
the Pope's partners.

00:05.561 --> 00:07.729
You seek an alliance
against Florence?

00:07.797 --> 00:09.164
How may we be of service?

00:09.231 --> 00:12.867
We will apply
unrelenting pressure

00:12.935 --> 00:14.903
until Lorenzo surrenders.

00:14.971 --> 00:18.540
You carry Giuliano's seed?
Yes, signora.

00:18.607 --> 00:20.809
So you will remain
with us.

00:20.876 --> 00:22.978
Are we on the right course?
We've been at sea for weeks.

00:23.045 --> 00:25.280
That, together with
this device,

00:25.348 --> 00:27.515
enabled me to estimate
the length of our voyage.

00:27.583 --> 00:29.017
If you're wrong,
we die at sea.

00:29.085 --> 00:30.518
We will not die at sea.

00:30.586 --> 00:32.554
What are you
teaching the boy?

00:32.621 --> 00:35.290
How to survive
when grace fails.

00:35.358 --> 00:37.826
This ship will sink without
Da Vinci at the helm.

00:37.893 --> 00:41.563
Storm on the way, Your Grace.
Could push us into the rocks.

00:42.531 --> 00:43.965
Let me out, please!

